adverse effect on Imprivata” means any effect that is or would reasonably be expected to become materially adverse to the business, financial condition or results of operations of Imprivata and its subsidiaries, taken as a whole.

However, the standard of “material adverse effect on Imprivata” excludes any adverse effect resulting from or arising out of:

